## Project Structure

```
src/filoma/
├── core/          # Backend integrations (fd, Rust)
├── directories/   # Directory analysis with 3 backends
├── files/         # File profiling and metadata
└── images/        # Image analysis (.tif, .png, .npy, .zarr)
```

